e skill, okay fine. They then make a list on how they could address the exploitation and they apply all the nerfs possible, when any 1 nerf would do.  Some of the high end mobs have a ton of hps as it is.  Its STUPID that 2 wizards that spent 23AA on this ability can't nuke the mob simultaneously.  Instead of all the damn nerfs, better to just make the skill disintegrate the mob if no other significant damage was done by other magics. Other classes can solo dragons, fight summoning mobs am I asking too much here? This AA ability needs to be revised or lowered in cost.  It was the signature for our class.  Plz don't let it die or be forgotten.  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=715698" target="top">Lobar of Karana</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
